Open Terminal
Type "cd /Applications/Discord.app/Contents/(your-mac-name-here)"
Hit Enter
Type "echo "MKL_DEBUG_CPU_TYPE=5 ./Discord" > discord_"
Now Right click on discord select show package contents open infoplist with a plist editor to make the change.
Follow these steps: 
Property List - "Executable file", Property Type - "String", Property Value - "discord_".
Save the plist and restart the discord.
Now you should be conncet normally.
